  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I mean, he was steering me in that direction, but was uncomfortable to tell me.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And you know, and the-- my final instructions were-- you know, when-- don't go with-- I mean, both my parents said this, and not during that hike that I took with my father, but subsequently.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You know, if-- don't talk to strangers.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Don't go with strangers.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And it wasn't necessarily stressed strange-- strange men, but just strangers.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But I think I-- you know, when I think back, I think I know what they were trying to tell me.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I really don't remember much about who I shared the compartment with or what happened on this trip.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But I know I immediately-- after I no longer could see my parents, I immediately got out some paper, and I started to write to my parents and to tell them what I was really feeling.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I'm glad that I was able to do this and that-- and I know they received those letters, because I wrote several.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "When the train stopped the first time in Cologne, I handed the letter to someone and asked them to please mail it.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And then it stopped again shortly before we crossed the border into Holland, and I, by that time, had another letter.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I-- my parents responded and told me that they had received those letters.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I'm glad I had the opportunity to tell them how much I understood that they loved me, and how much I loved them, and how much I knew that it was a great sacrifice that they had performed in letting me go.",
      "word_count": 42
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] We went to-- one of the-- as soon as the train crossed the border into Holland, it stopped somewhere.",
      "word_count": 23
    }
  ],
